Independiente Santa Fe [Bogotá] champions of Colombia 1975 


   Line-up of Independiente Santa Fe:  Luis Jerónimo López, José Antonio Tébez, Leonardo  
   Recúpero, Teófilo García, Darío López, Héctor Javier Céspedes, Antonio Rivas,
   Alonso "Cachaco" Rodríguez, Alfonso Cañón, Ernesto Díaz, Carlos Alberto Pandolfi.
   Coach: Francisco Hormazábal (Chile).  Manager: Raúl Araya.

  
   NOTE: Millonarios [Bogotá] was runner-up because they won in Torneo Apertura and finished
         second in Group A Torneo Clausura.


